column2: SELECT TOP # pa.z AS #, pa.ra, pa.dec, pa.psfMag_u AS #, pa.psfMag_g AS #, pa.psfMag_i AS #, pa.psfMag_r AS #, pa.psfMag_z AS # FROM SpecPhotoAll AS pa JOIN galSpecInfo AS gi ON pa.specObjID = gi.specObjID JOIN SpecObjAll AS sa ON pa.specObjID = sa.specObjID JOIN PhotoObjAll AS po ON sa.bestObjID = po.objID WHERE pa.class = # AND pa.z BETWEEN # AND # AND pa.psfMag_u IS NOT # AND pa.psfMag_g IS NOT # AND pa.psfMag_r IS NOT # AND pa.psfMag_i IS NOT # AND pa.psfMag_z IS NOT # AND pa.survey = # AND gi.primtarget > = # AND sa.targetType = # AND po.clean = # ORDER BY pa.z ASC;
